com.cyc.baseclient.subl.functions

Class FboundpFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.cycobject.DefaultCycObject
      • com.cyc.baseclient.subl.functions.FboundpFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CycObject, SubLFunction, Comparable<Object>

    public class FboundpFunction
extends DefaultCycObject
implements SubLFunction
    Represents FBOUNDP, which is used to check whether a symbol is bound to a function.

    To check if a variable is bound, see SubLFunctions.BOUNDP.

    Because this class underlies BasicSubLFunction.isBound(com.cyc.base.CycAccess), it does not extend that class or any of its sub-classes.
